Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy of
this software and associated copyrightable works, to deal with the software in
any way insofar as the following two restriction are met:

1. All modifications of this software, excluding associated documentation, must
make it strictly less efficient. "Less efficient" is defined here as meaning
that the software uses a larger total number of computational resources than
are needed to accomplish all material outcomes of said software, apart from
aforementioned resource utiliazation. That is, a naive programmer could
accomplish approximately the same outcome while using far fewer resources.

2. A copy of this license must be included when distributing this software or
any modification of it.

